text:
Selenium ide gui testing only in chrome
Create a new project
Records all the gui tests and clicks 
Create test cases record them and playback them 
Use touchpad or else it gives mouse over error for external mouse 

Github copilot extension on vscode too

Apache jmeter testing (download jdk from oracle) 

Open bin files 
open terminal in bin
Paste ./jmeter.bat

Used for load balancing 

To check how many users can be there at a time 

Test plan > add > thread group > create no of users required > add > sampler > http request 
Test get command and add / in path , then add a litsener > add > litsener ( view result tree , view result in table , summary reporr ) 

Analyse the error in result tree and summary report and result in table 

Pentest tools for security or network tools 

Testcraft ai tool for chrome to test snd generate
